(702, 39, 'admin', 'Four dead in Russian attack as diplomatic efforts to end war continue', '', '', 'four-dead-in-russian-attack-as-diplomatic-efforts-to-end-war-continue', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', '<div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"sc-3b6b161a-0 dPVOKT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: \"Times New Roman\"; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; display: grid; gap: 16px; width: 722px;\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">A Russian missile attack on the eastern Ukrainian city of Dnipro has killed four people and injured 40, authorities have said.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Unconfirmed reports say a ballistic missile was used in the strike, which took place on Monday morning.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Videos shared online showed a large explosion occur on the side of a motorway, and local media said an office block, cars and shops were hit or badly damaged.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Dnipro, which lies around 100km (62 miles) from the front line, has frequently come under Russian attack since the start of Moscow\'s full-scale invasion in February 2022.</p></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"sc-3b6b161a-0 dPVOKT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: \"Times New Roman\"; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; display: grid; gap: 16px; width: 722px;\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The attack came a day before US special envoy Steve Witkoff is due to meet President Vladimir Putin in Moscow for talks aimed at ending the war in Ukraine. Witkoff has visited the Russian president several times this year, but has never been to Kyiv.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">On Sunday, a Ukrainian delegation met Witkoff, US Secretary of State Marco Rubio and Donald Trump\'s son-in-law, Jared Kushner, in Florida.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Zelensky said on Monday that the talks had been \"very constructive\" but that there were some \"tough issues\" to be worked through - echoing Rubio\'s comments that the meeting had been \"productive\" but that there was \"more work to be done\".</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The Florida meeting was the latest step in weeks of intense \"shuttle diplomacy\" which saw Ukrainian and Russian delegations separately engage with US officials to discuss a peace plan.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Despite efforts, however, substantial differences remain between Moscow and Kyiv\'s positions.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Russia has refused to back down from its core demand that Ukraine retreats from the areas of the Donbas region it still holds, which Kyiv maintains it will never do.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">\"If they don\'t withdraw, we\'ll achieve this by force of arms,\" Vladimir Putin said. In response, Zelensky said that Russia \"scorned\" efforts \"to truly end the war\".</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Matters surrounding Ukraine\'s future security are also a source of contention. Kyiv and its European partners are keen for Ukraine to be given security guarantees - such as Nato membership - that would protect it from being attacked again.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">But Russia vehemently opposes this and Donald Trump too has ruled out allowing Ukraine to join the military alliance.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Meanwhile, Volodymyr Zelensky has arrived in Paris to rally support from French President Emmanuel Macron, and will head to Ireland on Tuesday.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">In recent weeks, concern has grown in Kyiv and among Europeans that the US was becoming more amenable to Russia\'s demands than Ukraine\'s, and that Europe was being excluded from the negotiating table.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Zelensky has also been weakened politically at home by a corruption scandal. His chief of staff Andriy Yermak, who had also led the Ukrainian delegation at peace talks, <a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cz0nljm4y74o\" class=\"sc-f9178328-0 iCaRzc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 26px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); text-decoration-line: underline; letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">resigned on Friday after anti-corruption investigators raided his home</a> - although he has not been accused of wrongdoing. Two cabinet ministers have also been fired.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">On Sunday Trump told reporters on Air Force One that Ukraine had \"some difficult little problems\", referring to the scandal, and repeated his view that both Russia and Ukraine wanted to end the war.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Tens of thousands of soldiers have been killed or injured, as well as thousands of civilians, and at least seven million people have become refugees, since Russia invaded on 24 February 2022.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \"BBC Reith Serif\", BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The conflict between the two ex-Soviet states stretches back to 2014 when Ukraine\'s pro-Russian president was overthrown and Russia responded by annexing Crimea and supporting armed uprisings in eastern Ukraine.</p></div>', '', 'Senin', '2025-12-01', '22:14:19', '025-12-01_221447.png', 4, 'lifestyle', 'Y'),
(705, 63, 'admin', 'Jury trial reforms set to be announced', '', '', 'jury-trial-reforms-set-to-be-announced', 'Y', 'N', 'Y', '<div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"sc-3b6b161a-0 dPVOKT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; display: grid; gap: 16px; width: 722px;\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The government is set to announce plans to restrict the right to a jury trial in England and Wales in an attempt to turn around unprecedented backlogs and delays in justice.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">David Lammy, the deputy prime minister and justice secretary, will lay out the proposals in Parliament later on Tuesday.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Last week his final \"decision\", contained in a document circulated around government, was leaked to the BBC and The Times.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">It is not clear if that plan - which would end jury trials other than for most serious cases including murder - has been approved by Cabinet or retreated from.</p></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"sc-3b6b161a-0 dPVOKT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; display: grid; gap: 16px; width: 722px;\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The proposals to cut jury trials are based on recommendations from a senior retired judge, who advised ministers that the reform would help tackle delays.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">There are currently 78,000 cases waiting to be completed in Crown Courts. In practice, this means that some suspects being charged with serious crimes today may not have a trial until late 2029 or early 2030. Officials predict the caseload will grow to more than 100,000 before then, unless there is further action.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Last week\'s leak of an internal government briefing&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cy7vdvrnnvzo\" class=\"sc-f9178328-0 iCaRzc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 26px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); text-decoration-line: underline; letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">showed final Ministry of Justice plans to create new forms of jury-less trials</a>, where cases would be decided by a judge alone. Jury trial would therefore end for the majority of crimes currently before Crown Courts - including theft, most drugs, violent and sexual offences and fraud.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Cases would only definitely go before a jury if the defendant was likely to be jailed for more than five years or was accused of murder, manslaughter or rape.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Volunteer magistrates - who handle the overwhelming majority of criminal cases in the lowest courts - would see their sentencing powers doubled to two years.</p></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"sc-3b6b161a-0 dPVOKT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; display: grid; gap: 16px; width: 722px;\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The leaked plan does not apply to Scotland or Northern Ireland and was circulated to other departments before final Cabinet sign off. It goes further than&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cm2m808kml0o\" class=\"sc-f9178328-0 iCaRzc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 26px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); text-decoration-line: underline; letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">recommendations earlier this year from retired Court of Appeal judge Sir Brian Leveson</a>.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Speaking ahead of the announcement in Parliament, Lammy declined to confirm the final package, but said there would be an extra £550m over three years for specialist victim support services - and £34m aimed at attracting more barristers into criminal work.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">\"Juries remain and will always remain a fundamental part of our justice system and play a very, very important role the decision,\" he said.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">\"[If] someone steals an iPhone from an electrical shop tomorrow - is it right that that individual should be able to opt for a jury?</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">\"That case will be in the system, it will be two or three days in court, and therefore delay the rape, the murder, the more serious offence.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">\"In all of the decisions that we\'re making, we are determined to put victims at the centre of the system and to balance those victims against the process.\"</p></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"sc-3b6b161a-0 dPVOKT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; display: grid; gap: 16px; width: 722px;\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">But Riel Karmy-Jones KC, chair of the Criminal Bar Association, said that it was not juries that had caused the unprecedented delays - but years of underfunding.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">\"Imposing an untried, untested layer of complexity and cost in the form of any new division of the Crown Court on our desperately underfunded system with its crumbling infrastructure is counter intuitive,\" she said.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Many criminal barristers blame the previous Conservative government for the backlogs - saying that the courts have been starved of resources for more than a decade.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Robert Jenrick MP, shadow justice secretary, said David Lammy had extensively defended juries in the past - and accused him of abandoning his principles.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">\"Labour have chosen to spend billions of extra pounds on benefits payments rather than funding the courts to get the backlog down,\" he said.</p></div>', 'The jury box at Court One of the Old Bailey', 'Selasa', '2025-12-02', '15:23:32', 'Screenshot_2025-12-02_152403.png', 2, 'international', 'Y'),
(706, 64, 'admin', 'Chinese and Japanese boats face off near disputed islands as feud worsens', '', '', 'chinese-and-japanese-boats-face-off-near-disputed-islands-as-feud-worsens', 'N', 'Y', 'Y', '<div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"sc-3b6b161a-0 dPVOKT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; display: grid; gap: 16px; width: 722px;\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">China and Japan\'s coast guards have given different accounts of a confrontation that occurred near a group of geopolitically sensitive islands in the East China Sea.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">China\'s Coast Guard said on Tuesday that a Japanese fishing vessel had illegally entered the waters of the Diaoyu Islands - which Tokyo calls the Senkaku Islands. China claims them as their territory, despite the islands being administered by Japan.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Japan\'s Coast Guard, meanwhile, said it intercepted and expelled two Chinese Coast Guard ships as they approached the fishing vessel.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The confrontation comes as&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/crklvx2n7rzo\" class=\"sc-f9178328-0 iCaRzc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 26px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); text-decoration-line: underline; letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">diplomatic ties between the two nations spiral</a>, after Japan\'s leader made controversial comments about Taiwan last month.</p></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"sc-3b6b161a-0 dPVOKT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; display: grid; gap: 16px; width: 722px;\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">While responding to a question in parliament last month, Japanese Prime Minister Sanae Takaichi, known to be a vocal critic of China and its activities in the region, suggested that Tokyo could take military action if Beijing attacked Taiwan.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Beijing views self-governed Taiwan as part of its territory and has not ruled out the use of force to \"reunite\" with it.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Both sides have since engaged in increasingly hostile rhetoric towards each other, with the widening rift affecting daily life for citizens in both countries.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Taiwan is located about 160km south-west of the Senkaku Islands.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">China Coast Guard (CCG) spokesperson Liu Dejun said that Chinese vessels on Tuesday approached and warned off a Japanese fishing boat that had \"illegally entered the territorial waters of China\'s Diaoyu Dao\", according to a state media report.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Liu added that the CCG took \"necessary law enforcement measures\", claiming that the islands were Chinese territory and urging Japan to \"immediately stop all acts of infringement and provocation in these waters\".</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The Japan Coast Guard (JCG) offered a slightly different account, saying they approached the Chinese vessels shortly after they were seen entering Japanese waters in the early hours of Tuesday and issued a demand that they leave the waters.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The JCG\'s patrol ship ensured the fishing boat\'s safety until the CCG left the territory a few hours later, it said.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">While Japan and China made an in-principle agreement in 2008 to jointly exploit resources in the East China Sea, the waterway that separates the two countries, tensions have escalated over the past decade-and-a-half.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The Senkaku/Diaoyu Islands, which are uninhabited,&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-pacific-11341139\" class=\"sc-f9178328-0 iCaRzc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 26px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); text-decoration-line: underline; letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">represent a flash point in these tensions</a>.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">China has sent an increasing number of ships towards the islands, in what appears to be an attempt to test Japan\'s resolve to defend them. Last year, the number of days Chinese government vessels were spotted in the territory hit a record high for the third consecutive year. There were also a record number of CCG vessels operating in the waters.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Prior the events of Tuesday morning, the CCG last entered the waters surrounding the Senkaku/Diaoyu Islands on 16 November, conducting what it described at the time as \"a lawful patrol operation conducted by the China coast guard to uphold its rights and</p></div>', 'The Senkaku/Diaoyu Islands have long been a source of tension between China and Japan', 'Selasa', '2025-12-02', '15:25:21', '2025-12-02_152619.png', 3, 'international,national', 'Y');
