(704, 62, 'admin', 'Starbucks to pay NYC workers $35m after alleged labour law violations', '', '', 'starbucks-to-pay-nyc-workers-35m-after-alleged-labour-law-violations', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"sc-3b6b161a-0 dPVOKT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; display: grid; gap: 16px; width: 722px;\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Starbucks has agreed pay more than $35m (£26m) to thousands of workers in New York City, to settle the city\'s claims that the company denied them stable schedules and arbitrarily slashed their hours.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Over 15,000 hourly workers are set to receive $50 for each week they worked during from July 2021 through July 2024, city officials said.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Vilda Vera Mayuga, commissioner of the New York City Department of Consumer and Worker Protection, cited alleged violations of city law requiring predictable schedules for workers.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The settlement, announced on Monday, comes as the coffee chain faces&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c5ype4j07xpo\" class=\"sc-f9178328-0 iCaRzc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 26px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); text-decoration-line: underline; letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">pressure to improve working conditions</a>&nbsp;nationwide.</p></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"sc-3b6b161a-0 dPVOKT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; display: grid; gap: 16px; width: 722px;\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Starbucks said in a statement that it is \"committed to creating the best job in retail and to ensuring our practices follow all laws\". It added that it has recently outlined plans to invest $500m to improve coffeehouse staffing and training.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Officials in New York City started investigating Starbucks in 2022 - a probe that began with dozens of worker complaints and grew to encompass all Starbucks locations across the city.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The city\'s worker protection department found \"a pattern of systemic violations\", officials said in a statement. Starbucks broke the city\'s Fair Workweek Law more than half a million times since 2021, they said, calling the agreement announced on Monday the largest worker protection settlement in the city\'s history.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">\"All workers deserve to be treated with dignity, and we are proud to stand up for our neighbors when a multibillion-dollar company like Starbucks chooses to systematically violate their employees\' rights,\" Mayuga said in a statement.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Under the terms of the agreement, Starbucks will also be forced to comply with the city\'s worker protection laws moving forward, which require fast food employers to give employees regular schedules and opportunities to take on extra shifts.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The company noted that New York City\'s worker protection laws are \"complex\".</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">\"We support the intent of the law and remain committed to compliance, but its complexity creates real-world challenges,\" Starbucks said. Compensation to employees in New York City will be for legal compliance, not unpaid wages, the chain said.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">New York City Mayor Eric Adams called it a \"landmark settlement\" that will \"put tens of millions of dollars back into the pockets of hard-working New Yorkers and reinforce every New Yorker\'s right to a reliable schedule, full hours, and basic dignity\".</p></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"sc-3b6b161a-0 dPVOKT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; display: grid; gap: 16px; width: 722px;\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Starbucks has in recent years faced consumer boycotts, a wave of new competitors and a customer backlash over high prices, as well as turmoil in its leadership ranks.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The chain, under chief executive Brian Niccol, has been working to bring back customers, promising faster service and a return its coffeehouse roots, with ceramic mugs and hand-written notes. In October, Starbucks reported 1% growth in sales at global stores open at least one year - its first quarterly increase in almost two years. But in the US, sales were flat.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Despite some recent progress in boosting sales, the company is still wrestling with a years-long labour fight that threatens to hamper its turnaround. It remains at odds with the Starbucks Workers United union over pay, staffing and hundreds of unresolved charges of unfair labour practice.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Last month, workers represented by Starbucks Workers United&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cwy7r48g0zlo\" class=\"sc-f9178328-0 iCaRzc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 26px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); text-decoration-line: underline; letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">went on a strike in their latest bid</a>&nbsp;to pressure the coffee chain for better pay and staffing after negotiations stalled.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">\"When this company cuts our hours, understaffs our stores and busts our union, it makes it harder for us to do our job and create that great experience for customers,\" Kai Fritz, a union barista, said in a statement on Monday after New York City officials announced their agreement with the company.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">\"This settlement is a step in the right direction.\"</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The worker walkout is ongoing and has expanded to more than 120 stores across 85 cities, Starbucks Workers United said. The union has won elections at roughly 5% of the chain\'s company-owned US locations since launching four years ago.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Thousands of workers remain on strike - in New York City and beyond - to demand a \"fair union contract that memorializes job protections, better staffing, and higher pay\", Lynne Fox, Workers United\'s international president, said in a statement.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">\"For too long, Starbucks has acted with impunity: manipulating schedules, disrespecting workers, and ignoring legal protections put into place by New Yorkers to protect working people from unfair business practices,\" Ms Fox said.</p></div>', '', 'Selasa', '2025-12-02', '15:21:30', 'Screenshot_2025-12-02_152207.png', 0, 'lifestyle,international', 'Y'),
(707, 65, 'admin', 'More than 70,000 killed in Gaza since Israel offensive began, Hamas-run health ministry says', '', '', 'more-than-70000-killed-in-gaza-since-israel-offensive-began-hamasrun-health-ministry-says', 'Y', 'Y', 'Y', '<div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"sc-3b6b161a-0 dPVOKT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; display: grid; gap: 16px; width: 722px;\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">More than 70,000 Palestinians have been killed as a result of Israel\'s military campaign in Gaza, according to the territory\'s Hamas-run health ministry.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The death toll has continued to rise since a ceasefire took effect on 10 October, with Israel carrying out air strikes for what it says are violations of the truce - while bodies continue to be recovered from under the rubble.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Among those reportedly killed in an Israeli drone strike on Saturday were two young brothers, Fadi and Juma Abu Assi, whose family said they had been gathering firewood when they were killed.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The Israel Defense Forces (IDF) told the BBC they had struck two suspects who had crossed the so-called yellow line.</p></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"sc-3b6b161a-0 dPVOKT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; display: grid; gap: 16px; width: 722px;\"><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The line marks where the Israeli military agreed to withdraw to under a ceasefire brokered by the United States more than seven weeks ago.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The boys who died have been described in media reports as an eight-year-old and his brother, aged 10 or 11.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Relatives said the children had been looking for firewood east of Khan Younis in the southern Gaza Strip when they were killed.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Their funeral was held at Nasser Hospital on Saturday.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Figures from the Gaza Ministry of Health (MoH) have been widely used throughout the war and are seen as reliable by the United Nations (UN) and international institutions. But Israel has consistently disputed data published by Gaza\'s authorities.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">International journalists, including the BBC, are blocked by Israel from entering Gaza independently, so are unable to verify figures from either side.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">Gaza\'s Health Ministry says the Palestinian toll is now 70,100 and that more than 350 of those deaths have happened since the 10 October ceasefire.</p><p class=\"sc-9a00e533-0 eZyhnA\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;BBC Reith Serif&quot;, BBCReithSerif-fallback, serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(32, 34, 36); letter-spacing: -0.36px;\">The Israeli military launched its offensive on Gaza in response to the Hamas-led attack on southern Israel on 7 October 2023, in which about 1,200 people were killed and 251 others were taken hostage.</p></div>', 'A funeral was held at Gaza\'s Nasser Hospital for the two young boys killed in an Israeli strike on Saturday', 'Selasa', '2025-12-02', '15:27:47', '2025-12-02_152827.png', 4, 'international', 'Y'),
(708, 54, 'admin', 'Ex-England player arrested on suspicion of attempted rape', '', '', 'exengland-player-arrested-on-suspicion-of-attempted-rape', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span class=\"ssrcss-1xjjfut-BoldText e5tfeyi3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bolder; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">A former England and Premier League footballer has been arrested on suspicion of attempted rape.</span></p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">The suspect, who played for the England in the 2010s, was detained at Stansted Airport, reported The Sun.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">He cannot be named for legal reasons.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">\"A man has been arrested on suspicion of attempted rape and has been bailed to a date in late February 2026 while we continue our enquiries,\" said an Essex Police spokesperson.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">The player was said to have been stopped at a passport control point by Border Force guards before he could board a flight on Sunday.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">His details showed he was wanted by police over a non-recent allegation of attempted rape, according to The Sun.</p>', 'he former Premier League footballer was reportedly arrested at Stansted Airport in Essex on Sunday', 'Selasa', '2025-12-02', '21:15:05', '2025-12-02_211611.png', 1, 'lifestyle', 'Y');
