vertical-align: baseline;\">The top two teams from each pool will progress to the round of 16 along with the four best third-place nations. This is where it gets a bit more complicated...</p><div class=\"ssrcss-h5qd1q-ListContainer e5tfeyi0\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><ul role=\"list\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The top team in Pools A, B, C and D will face teams that finished third in their group</p></li><li style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The winners of Pools E and F will play the runners-up from Pools D and B</p></li><li style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The runners-up from Pools A and C will then take on the runners-up from Pools E and F</p></li></ul></div><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Some have said the format is imbalanced, but organisers say this is \"addressed in the next round\" and will even itself out.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">So for example, the winner of Pool A will play a third-place team in the round of 16, but could face the winner of Pool B if that team advances. The winner of Pool E will play a second-place team in both knockout rounds.</p></div></div><div data-component=\"subheadline-block\" class=\"ssrcss-1o1fzgd-ComponentWrapper-HeadlineComponentWrapper egtrm1f0\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><h2 id=\"Why-is-the-Rugby-World-Cup-draw-done-so-early\" tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"ssrcss-pbttu9-Heading e10rt3ze0\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.125; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: \"ss01\" 0; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><span role=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Why is the Rugby World Cup draw done so early?</span></h2></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-suhx0k-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-1o5p6v2-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">It is not uncommon for World Rugby to host the draw years before the tournament. The pools for the 2023 World Cup were decided in December 2020, for example.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">That draw caused controversy as the world\'s five best ranked teams in 2023 - Ireland, France, New Zealand, South Africa and Scotland - ended up on the same side of the draw because of their rankings at the time of the draw three years earlier.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The 2027 draw is being conducted closer to the tournament this time. This is to:</p><div class=\"ssrcss-h5qd1q-ListContainer e5tfeyi0\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><ul role=\"list\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Reflect current form and rankings halfway through the international cycle</p></li><li style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Help fans and teams make travel and accommodation arrangements</p></li><li style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Give organisers time to stage a successful tournament</p></li><li style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Allow host cities and states time to engage with local communities</p></li></ul></div></div></div><div data-component=\"subheadline-block\" class=\"ssrcss-1o1fzgd-ComponentWrapper-HeadlineComponentWrapper egtrm1f0\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><h2 id=\"Where-are-the-Rugby-World-Cup-host-cities\" tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"ssrcss-pbttu9-Heading e10rt3ze0\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.125; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: \"ss01\" 0; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><span role=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Where are the Rugby World Cup host cities?</span></h2></div><div data-component=\"text-block\" class=\"ssrcss-suhx0k-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 36.25rem; color: rgb(20, 20, 20);\"><div class=\"ssrcss-1o5p6v2-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The tournament will be hosted in seven cities across Australia.</p><div class=\"ssrcss-h5qd1q-ListContainer e5tfeyi0\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-