ph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Perth, Western Australia</p></li><li style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: flex;\"><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Sydney, New South Wales</p></li></ul></div><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The full match schedule will be announced on 3 December, with pre-sale tickets for registered fans available from 18 February 2026.</p></div></div>', '', 'Selasa', '2025-12-02', '21:35:47', '2025-12-02_213751.png', 1, 'lifestyle', 'Y'),
(713, 54, 'admin', 'Ex-England player arrested on suspicion of attempted rape', '', '', 'exengland-player-arrested-on-suspicion-of-attempted-rape', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\"><span class=\"ssrcss-1xjjfut-BoldText e5tfeyi3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bolder; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">A former England and Premier League footballer has been arrested on suspicion of attempted rape.</span></p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">The suspect, who played for the England in the 2010s, was detained at Stansted Airport, reported The Sun.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">He cannot be named for legal reasons.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">\"A man has been arrested on suspicion of attempted rape and has been bailed to a date in late February 2026 while we continue our enquiries,\" said an Essex Police spokesperson.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">The player was said to have been stopped at a passport control point by Border Force guards before he could board a flight on Sunday.</p><p class=\"ssrcss-1q0x1qg-Paragraph e1jhz7w10\" style=\"margin: 16px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: ReithSans, Helvetica, Arial, freesans, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(20, 20, 20); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246);\">His details showed he was wanted by police over a non-recent allegation of attempted rape, according to The Sun.</p>', 'he former Premier League footballer was reportedly arrested at Stansted Airport in Essex on Sunday', 'Selasa', '2025-12-02', '21:15:05', '2025-12-02_211611.png', 1, 'lifestyle', 'Y'),
(714, 54, 'admin', 'Top Serie A striker suffers ankle injury during training', '', '', 'top-serie-a-striker-suffers-ankle-injury-during-training', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A leading Serie A striker has reportedly picked up an ankle injury during a closed training session on Thursday.</p>\r\n<p>Club medical staff confirmed the player will undergo further scans to determine the full extent of the damage.</p>\r\n<p>The injury occurred after a collision during a high-intensity drill. Early reports suggest he could miss several upcoming league fixtures.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '20:31:00', 'europeana-6v0XWXLidWU-unsplash.jpg', 1, 'lifestyle,international', 'Y'),
(715, 54, 'admin', 'Premier League club pursuing shock January move for young midfielder', '', '', 'premier-league-club-pursuing-shock-january-move-for-young-midfielder', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A mid-table Premier League side is reportedly preparing a surprising January transfer approach for a highly rated young midfielder.</p>\r\n<p>The 21-year-old has impressed scouts with his recent performances, prompting growing interest from English clubs.</p>\r\n<p>Negotiations are expected to begin within the next two weeks.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '20:31:10', 'benjamin-elliott-Uv3MRbZzZvU-unsplash.jpg', 1, 'national', 'Y'),
(716, 54, 'admin', 'Late goal sends European giant into Champions League knockout stage', '', '', 'late-goal-sends-european-giant-into-champions-league-knockout-stage', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A dramatic late goal secured qualification for one of Europe\'s powerhouse clubs in the Champions League on Wednesday night.</p>\r\n<p>The match remained level until stoppage time, when a substitute forward found the net with a low drive.</p>\r\n<p>The win guarantees top spot in their group with one game remaining.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '20:31:18', 'joshua-hoehne-tIXiG8S5-aI-unsplash.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(717, 54, 'admin', 'Manager insists team “will not panic” despite poor run of results', '', '', 'manager-insists-team-“will-not-panic”-despite-poor-run-of-results', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>The head coach of a major European team has urged supporters to stay calm following a series of disappointing league results.</p>\r\n<p>Speaking at a press conference, he stated that the squad remains united and focused on improvement.</p>\r\n<p>He added that tactical adjustments will be made ahead of their next match.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '20:31:25', 'lena-polishko-QjnjCLTM4eU-unsplash.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(718, 54, 'admin', 'Top defender set to sign new long-term contract with his club', '', '', 'top-defender-set-to-sign-new-longterm-contract-with-his-club', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A star defender is close to signing a new long-term contract after weeks of negotiations with his club.</p>\r\n<p>Sources say both sides have agreed on personal terms and only final paperwork is pending.</p>\r\n<p>The renewal is expected to be officially announced within the next few days.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '20:31:34', 'constantin-shim-6JyhQyceWy8-unsplash.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(719, 34, 'admin', 'Top cyclist withdraws from major tour due to illness', '', '', 'top-cyclist-withdraws-from-major-tour-due-to-illness', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A leading rider has withdrawn from an upcoming major cycling tour after being diagnosed with a viral illness.</p>\r\n<p>The team confirmed the decision, stating that the rider’s health remains the priority.</p>\r\n<p>He is expected to return to competition early next year.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '20:51:01', 'aditya-wardhana-LFv9vVBLmwM-unsplash1.jpg', 0, '', 'Y');
INSERT INTO `berita` (`id_berita`, `id_kategori`, `username`, `judul`, `sub_judul`, `youtube`, `judul_seo`, `headline`, `aktif`, `utama`, `isi_berita`, `keterangan_gambar`, `hari`, `tanggal`, `jam`, `gambar`, `dibaca`, `tag`, `status`) VALUES
(720, 34, 'admin', 'New climbing specialist shines during mountain training camp', '', '', 'new-climbing-specialist-shines-during-mountain-training-camp', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A young climber impressed coaches during a week-long mountain training camp in the Alps.</p>\r\n<p>His exceptional endurance and explosive acceleration caught the attention of several WorldTour teams.</p>\r\n<p>He is expected to be included in the roster for next season\'s major tours.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '20:51:15', 'yns-plt-NY1D4Zni7fc-unsplash.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(721, 37, 'admin', 'National sprinter sets personal best in 100m warm-up event', '', '', 'national-sprinter-sets-personal-best-in-100m-warmup-event', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A national-level sprinter clocked a new personal best during a warm-up event ahead of the regional championships.</p>\r\n<p>The athlete attributed the improvement to changes in sprint mechanics and strength training.</p>\r\n<p>His coach believes he is on track for a podium finish.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '20:51:40', 'braden-collum-9HI8UJMSdZA-unsplash1.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(722, 37, 'admin', 'Long-distance runner announces surprise early-season return', '', '', 'longdistance-runner-announces-surprise-earlyseason-return', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A prominent long-distance runner has confirmed an earlier-than-expected return to competition.</p>\r\n<p>The athlete had been recovering from a foot injury suffered in mid-2025.</p>\r\n<p>He will participate in a half-marathon event as part of his comeback schedule.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '20:52:02', 'joshua-burdick-qBOsOPO4Uzc-unsplash.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(723, 46, 'admin', 'Rising star leads opening round of international golf championship', '', '', 'rising-star-leads-opening-round-of-international-golf-championship', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A rising star produced a stunning performance to lead the opening round of a major international golf tournament.</p>\r\n<p>Strong winds made conditions difficult, but he maintained consistency throughout the day.</p>\r\n<p>He heads into the second round with a two-shot advantage.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '20:52:25', 'mk-s-WHf1wtNMMLU-unsplash1.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(724, 46, 'admin', 'Veteran golfer announces retirement after final season tour', '', '', 'veteran-golfer-announces-retirement-after-final-season-tour', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A veteran golfer has officially announced his retirement following the conclusion of his farewell tour.</p>\r\n<p>With over two decades of professional experience, he leaves behind an impressive legacy.</p>\r\n<p>The golfing world has praised his sportsmanship and impact on the sport.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '20:52:44', 'public-domain-vectors-uNXSBzXhfMM-unsplash1.jpg', 1, '', 'Y'),
(725, 48, 'admin', 'Teenage sensation upset veteran star in dramatic three-set match', '', '', 'teenage-sensation-upset-veteran-star-in-dramatic-threeset-match', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A teenage tennis prodigy produced a major upset after defeating a seasoned veteran in a thrilling three-set battle.</p>\r\n<p>The match featured multiple momentum shifts and high-intensity rallies.</p>\r\n<p>The youngster moves on to her first tour-level quarterfinal.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '20:53:25', 'aleksandar-kyng-dhkdfFxGHfU-unsplash1.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(726, 48, 'admin', 'Top seed advances to semifinal after straight-set victory', '', '', 'top-seed-advances-to-semifinal-after-straightset-victory', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>The tournament’s top seed secured a place in the semifinals after a dominant straight-set win.</p>\r\n<p>She showcased powerful baseline shots and near-perfect serve accuracy.</p>\r\n<p>Her next opponent is expected to pose a tougher challenge.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '20:53:05', 'round-icons-kX4zeH8RN34-unsplash1.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(727, 52, 'admin', 'Rookie driver earns first career podium after chaotic grand prix', '', '', 'rookie-driver-earns-first-career-podium-after-chaotic-grand-prix', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A rookie Formula 1 driver claimed his first podium finish following a dramatic and incident-filled grand prix.</p>\r\n<p>Multiple safety cars and unpredictable weather created a challenging race environment.</p>\r\n<p>The young driver described the result as a “dream moment”.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '20:54:09', 'appic-I_nDdpCM2bw-unsplash1.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(728, 52, 'admin', 'Leading F1 team introduces upgraded front wing ahead of final races', '', '', 'leading-f1-team-introduces-upgraded-front-wing-ahead-of-final-races', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A top Formula 1 team has unveiled a newly designed front wing as part of its push for late-season performance gains.</p>\r\n<p>Engineers claim the upgrade will offer improved corner stability and aerodynamic efficiency.</p>\r\n<p>The part will debut during practice sessions this weekend.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '20:53:48', 'roy-tsong-W0haDrVTW58-unsplash.jpg', 1, '', 'Y'),
(729, 66, 'admin', 'Major tech firm announces $2 billion investment in Southeast Asia', '', '', 'major-tech-firm-announces-2-billion-investment-in-southeast-asia', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A leading global technology company has revealed plans to invest $2 billion in Southeast Asia over the next three years.</p>\r\n<p>The investment will focus on cloud infrastructure, digital training programs, and support for regional startups.</p>\r\n<p>Industry experts say the move highlights the region’s growing importance as a strategic digital hub.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '21:13:10', 'willy-the-wizard-8bWvdH7YxRw-unsplash1.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(730, 66, 'admin', 'Global markets slip as investors await key interest rate decision', '', '', 'global-markets-slip-as-investors-await-key-interest-rate-decision', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>Global stock markets experienced slight declines on Thursday as investors turned cautious ahead of a major interest rate announcement.</p>\r\n<p>Analysts predict that central banks may keep rates steady, but concerns about slowing economic growth continue to weigh on sentiment.</p>\r\n<p>Traders are expected to remain on edge until the final decision is published later this week.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '21:12:41', 'luky-triohandoko-eecTcKqXpz8-unsplash1.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(731, 19, 'admin', 'Global PC shipments rise for the first time in three years', '', '', 'global-pc-shipments-rise-for-the-first-time-in-three-years', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>Worldwide PC shipments have grown again after nearly three years of decline, according to new market research data.</p>\r\n<p>The rebound is attributed to strong demand for productivity devices and the adoption of AI-powered laptops.</p>\r\n<p>Analysts expect continued growth through 2026.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '21:21:48', 'sasha-lend-27_mAh9a49U-unsplash1.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(732, 19, 'admin', 'New smartphone chip promises major performance boost', '', '', 'new-smartphone-chip-promises-major-performance-boost', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A leading semiconductor company has unveiled its latest smartphone processor, claiming significant improvements in speed and energy efficiency.</p>\r\n<p>The new chip features an upgraded neural engine, enabling faster on-device AI tasks and improved battery life.</p>\r\n<p>Flagship devices using this chip are expected to launch early next year.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '21:21:10', 'tasha-kostyuk-roPGTtmZZ5U-unsplash1.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(733, 67, 'admin', 'Scientists discover potential treatment targeting early-stage cancer', '', '', 'scientists-discover-potential-treatment-targeting-earlystage-cancer', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>Researchers have identified a new compound that shows promise in targeting early-stage cancer cells with minimal side effects.</p>\r\n<p>The treatment works by interrupting key proteins that help tumors grow, potentially opening doors for less invasive therapies.</p>\r\n<p>Clinical trials are expected to begin next year.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '21:24:02', 'vitaly-gariev-Tn0fjekZemA-unsplash1.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(734, 67, 'admin', 'New study links improved sleep habits to stronger immune system', '', '', 'new-study-links-improved-sleep-habits-to-stronger-immune-system', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A recently published study suggests that consistent sleep routines may significantly enhance the body’s immune response.</p>\r\n<p>Researchers found that adults who slept between seven and nine hours showed better resistance to seasonal infections.</p>\r\n<p>The study encourages adopting healthier sleep patterns to support long-term wellbeing.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '21:23:20', 'nur-asyrof-E0y4F-pyR2I-unsplash1.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(735, 68, 'admin', 'Researchers develop AI that can learn tasks with minimal data', '', '', 'researchers-develop-ai-that-can-learn-tasks-with-minimal-data', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A team of computer scientists has created a new AI model capable of learning complex tasks using far fewer training examples than traditional systems.</p>\r\n<p>This breakthrough could reduce the cost of developing AI applications and speed up innovation in multiple industries.</p>\r\n<p>The model is expected to see early real-world testing in 2026.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '21:26:08', 'hendi-perkasa-xFpGoTDffyc-unsplash1.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(736, 68, 'admin', 'AI-powered tool detects cyber threats faster than traditional systems', '', '', 'aipowered-tool-detects-cyber-threats-faster-than-traditional-systems', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p>A new AI-driven cybersecurity platform has been introduced, capable of identifying cyber threats in real time.</p>\r\n<p>The system analyzes massive data streams and flags suspicious behavior within seconds, reducing the risk of major breaches.</p>\r\n<p>Experts say the technology could transform corporate security operations.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '21:25:20', 'manuel-campagnoli-Qwbfa93g_L0-unsplash1.jpg', 0, '', 'Y'),
(737, 2, 'admin', 'Manchester City confirm star striker sidelined for six weeks with ankle injury', '', '', 'manchester-city-confirm-star-striker-sidelined-for-six-weeks-with-ankle-injury', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p><strong>Manchester City have confirmed that their leading striker will be out of action for at least six weeks following an ankle injury sustained during training on Wednesday.</strong></p>\r\n<p>The club released a statement saying the medical team has advised a full rehabilitation program, ruling the player out of City\'s upcoming Premier League and Champions League fixtures.</p>\r\n<p>Pep Guardiola expressed concern but remained optimistic about the striker\'s recovery timeline, stating that the squad will adapt and push forward despite the setback.</p>\r\n<p>The injury comes at a crucial stage of the season as City continue to compete on multiple fronts, increasing pressure on the remaining forwards in the squad.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '01:22:00', '', 1, '', 'N'),
(738, 2, 'admin', 'Real Madrid close to securing €85m midfielder as January transfer window approaches', '', '', 'real-madrid-close-to-securing-85m-midfielder-as-january-transfer-window-approaches', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p><strong>Real Madrid are reportedly finalizing negotiations to sign a highly rated European midfielder in an €85 million deal ahead of the January transfer window.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Spanish media outlets claim the club has reached an agreement in principle with the player, who has been on Carlo Ancelotti\'s radar since last season.</p>\r\n<p>The midfielder is expected to complete medical tests in the coming weeks, with the official announcement anticipated before the winter market opens.</p>\r\n<p>If completed, the signing would add significant depth to Madrid\'s midfield and strengthen their long-term project as they continue their push for La Liga and Champions League success.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '01:23:00', '', 1, '', 'N'),
(739, 21, 'admin', 'Global oil prices fall as demand slows heading into 2026', '', '', 'global-oil-prices-fall-as-demand-slows-heading-into-2026', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p><strong>Global oil prices dropped nearly 3% on Thursday as demand indicators showed signs of weakening toward the end of 2025.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Analysts say slowing industrial output in several major economies contributed to the decline, raising concerns about market stability.</p>\r\n<p>Energy firms remain cautious as they prepare for potential volatility in early 2026.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '09:11:00', '', 1, '', 'N'),
(740, 21, 'admin', 'Indonesia’s digital banking sector sees record growth in Q4', '', '', 'indonesias-digital-banking-sector-sees-record-growth-in-q4', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p><strong>Indonesia’s digital banking platforms reported a record surge in new users during Q4 2025.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Financial experts attribute the rise to improved mobile services and increased public trust in online banking systems.</p>\r\n<p>Regulators expect the sector to continue expanding rapidly through 2026.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '09:13:00', '', 1, '', 'N'),
(741, 22, 'admin', 'Parliament debates new transparency bill amid rising public pressure', '', '', 'parliament-debates-new-transparency-bill-amid-rising-public-pressure', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p><strong>The national parliament opened discussions on a new transparency bill aimed at increasing public access to government data.</strong></p>\r\n<p>The proposal has gained strong support following months of public demand for greater accountability.</p>\r\n<p>Lawmakers are expected to vote on the bill early next year.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '10:02:00', '', 1, '', 'N'),
(742, 22, 'admin', 'Regional leaders meet to discuss 2026 security cooperation framework', '', '', 'regional-leaders-meet-to-discuss-2026-security-cooperation-framework', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p><strong>Leaders from multiple provinces gathered on Thursday to discuss a new security cooperation plan for 2026.</strong></p>\r\n<p>The meeting focused on joint intelligence sharing, border monitoring, and emergency response coordination.</p>\r\n<p>Officials say the framework could be finalized by March 2026.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '10:04:00', '', 1, '', 'N'),
(743, 23, 'admin', 'Popular singer announces world tour dates for 2026', '', '', 'popular-singer-announces-world-tour-dates-for-2026', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p><strong>A globally acclaimed singer has revealed official dates for a massive world tour scheduled for 2026.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Fans across Asia, Europe, and North America will have the chance to attend the highly anticipated concerts.</p>\r\n<p>Tickets are expected to sell out within hours once released.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '11:20:00', '', 1, '', 'N'),
(744, 23, 'admin', 'New sci-fi film breaks streaming records within first 24 hours', '', '', 'new-sci-fi-film-breaks-streaming-records-within-first-24-hours', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p><strong>A newly released sci-fi film has shattered streaming platform records, drawing millions of viewers in a single day.</strong></p>\r\n<p>The film\'s strong visuals and storyline received widespread praise from critics and audiences alike.</p>\r\n<p>producers announced plans for a sequel next year.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '11:22:00', '', 1, '', 'N'),
(745, 31, 'admin', 'New study links consistent sleep patterns to improved mental health', '', '', 'new-study-links-consistent-sleep-patterns-to-improved-mental-health', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p><strong>Researchers have found that maintaining a consistent sleep schedule significantly improves mental well-being.</strong></p>\r\n<p>The findings highlight the need for better sleep hygiene among adults and teenagers.</p>\r\n<p>Experts recommend reducing screen time before bed to improve sleep quality.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '12:05:00', '', 1, '', 'N'),
(746, 31, 'admin', 'Health ministry warns of rising flu cases ahead of rainy season', '', '', 'health-ministry-warns-of-rising-flu-cases-ahead-of-rainy-season', 'N', 'N', 'N', '<p><strong>The health ministry issued an alert on Thursday after a rise in flu cases was recorded in several regions.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Officials advise citizens to practice hygiene measures and seek early treatment when symptoms appear.</p>\r\n<p>The ministry also urged high-risk groups to get vaccinated.</p>', '', 'Kamis', '2025-12-04', '12:09:00', '', 1, '', 'N');

